Uses of Package
de.hsb.ms.syn.common.audio

  • Packages that use de.hsb.ms.syn.common.audio 
    Package Description
    de.hsb.ms.syn.common.audio
    Abstract AudioAlgorithm classes and its linked resource classes (Scale, Properties) providing the base for the audio processing that takes place in this application.
    de.hsb.ms.syn.common.audio.fx
    AudioAlgorithm implementations of sound manipulative effects.
    de.hsb.ms.syn.common.audio.gen
    AudioAlgorithm implementations of sound generators.
    de.hsb.ms.syn.common.ui
    Custom user interface element classes used by either the Desktop host or mobile devices.
    de.hsb.ms.syn.common.util
    Utility classes and a Constants dump class.
    de.hsb.ms.syn.common.vo
    Node classes used by the Desktop host to represent sound entities, which are also capable of arranging themselves along sound paths.
  • Classes in de.hsb.ms.syn.common.audio used by de.hsb.ms.syn.common.audio 
    Class and Description
    AudioAlgorithm
    Base class for Delegate algorithms used by both GenNode and FXNode instances It is extended by FXDelegate and GenDelegate
    Properties
    Each algorithm that is assigned to a DraggableNode holds an instance of this class, which encapsulates necessary parameters for the algorithm.
    Property
    Data structure for one property of a DraggableNode's AudioAlgorithm.
    Scale
    This class represents the musical scale corresponding to a GenNode.
